
Supermart Grocery Sales Retail Analysis
Project Overview

This project analyzes grocery retail sales data using Power BI. The dashboard helps understand sales performance, profit trends, customer orders, regional performance, and category-wise sales distribution. The goal is to provide useful business insights for better decision-making.

Objectives
Analyze total sales, profit, and orders.
Identify top-performing regions and cities.
Compare sales across different product categories and subcategories.
Track monthly sales trends.
Measure profit margins and discounts.
Tools Used
Power BI Desktop
Data Cleaning and Transformation using Power Query
Data Visualization using Charts, Cards, and Slicers
