Key Insights
West region generated the highest sales.
North region recorded the lowest sales.
Soft Drinks and Health Drinks contributed the highest profits.
Sales increased significantly during October, November, and December.
Kanyakumari recorded the highest number of orders among cities.
Overall profit margin remained at 25%.
Conclusion

The Power BI dashboard provides a clear view of sales and profit performance across regions, categories, and cities. The insights help businesses identify profitable products, high-performing regions, and seasonal sales trends, supporting data-driven business decisions.

